hadows with their very presence.  Selfish beasts...never tire...always taking never giving...draining me...twisting the path until it's tangled beyond my comprehension, beyond the norm, beyond what any mortal man should tread.  It's voice a constant reminder that a sickening presence like that really can exist...and it's breath sends numbing pains of hate...fear....uncomfort through me always.  I want to engulf myself in a blaze of fire for a little while to keep the shadows back.  I'll burn but I'll be free of the confusion and sadness that the shadows bring.  They'll all go away and I can lie in my ashes and remember a time when i wasn't burnt and the blackness was still foreign to me.  But that's a fork in the road that tempts me, but I fear to take.  <br><br>Ignorance is a blanket that, if used correctly, may assist in the living of the present.  You must know how to use this before you try though, nothing saddens us all then a poor use of ignorance.<br><br>Drowning...<br><br>   <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub76.ezboard.com/fthemissednotethestage.showPrevMessage?topicID=196.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub76.ezboard.com/fthemissednotethestage.showNextMessage?topicID=196.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub76.ezboard.com/fthemissednotethestage.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=196.topic><img src=http://ezsasi.homestead.com/files/MissedNote/TReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub76.ezboard.com/fthemissednotethestage.threadControl?topicID=196.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub76.ezboard.com/fthemissednotethestage.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=196.topic>Subscri